Package ar.edu.utn.frc.tup.lc.iv.services.impl

Class ChargeServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
ar.edu.utn.frc.tup.lc.iv.services.impl.ChargeServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
ChargeService
@Service public class ChargeServiceImpl extends Object implements ChargeService
Implementation of the ChargeService interface.

This class contains the business logic for charge management, including methods to add fines, services and retrieve them based on various criteria such as date, year and by lot.
